10
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:24,560
Did he really start that fire?

11
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,120
Yes.

12
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,680
Master.

13
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:34,560
Is he really so heartless?

14
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:37,520
Your daughter went into
the fire to save you.

15
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,040
How is she?

16
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:47,840
The fire was too fierce,
so I could only save you. She...

17
00:02:55,240 --> 00:03:00,360
No, no.

18
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:04,560
Qi!

19
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,440
- Someone.
- Here.

20
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,480
Here.

21
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,760
Sir, are we not saving Lady Yunqi?

22
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:31,640
If Du Ruomei learns Prime Minister
not only sent someone to kill her,

23
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,200
but also got Su Yunqi killed,

24
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:35,000
she must hate Prime Minister

25
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,720
and will tell us everything she knows.

26
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,000
However...

27
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:43,240
Once we join the Armor Guard,
we become ruthless demons.

28
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:47,640
Being softened can be lethal.

29
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:53,200
Didn't he say not to save her?
Being softened can be lethal?

30
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,640
Quite ruthless.

31
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,680
Do you still want
to keep secrets for such a man?

32
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,520
He even wanted
to get your daughter killed.

33
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,640
Don't you want him to suffer?

34
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:25,840
I'll tell you. I...

35
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,320
Where is my mother?

36
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,040
Mrs. Du, be careful.

37
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,360
The Book of Fate.

38
