Mother.

47
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,440
Mother.

48
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,000
Yunqi.

49
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,520
Yunqi.

50
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,440
Chase!

51
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,400
Yes.

52
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,000
Mother.

53
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,320
Mother.

54
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:05,760
Mother.

55
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:15,232
Qi, you must become...

56
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:21,760
Become the princess,

57
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:28,200
so you can protect yourself.

58
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,560
Mother.

59
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,120
Mother.

60
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:00,080
Why?

61
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:07,040
Why are you doing this to us?

62
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:12,120
What did we do wrong?

63
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:46,320
Tell me who sent you?

64
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,560
Tell me.

65
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,680
It was Prime Minister.

66
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,440
Why?

67
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:07,840
Because Mrs. Du knew too much.

68
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:43,240
Hold the knife firmly for killing.

69
00:10:06,308 --> 00:10:08,224
(Condolence)

70
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:17,120
Yunqi, your mother was morally corrupt.

71
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:22,920
I have treated her well
for allowing you to mourn her here.

72
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,080
Do not blame me.

73
00:10:31,652 --> 00:10:33,568
(Condolence)

74
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,720
My mother was with you for years.

75
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,680
She couldn't even
have a memorial tablet now.

76
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,720
Is that how you treat her well?

77
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,920
How can you speak to me like this?

78
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,760
Sister, don't argue with Father anymore.

79
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:01,920
We should keep peace.

80
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,320
Do you know how my mother died?

81
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:09,560
In the Lu Mansion,
bandits caused trouble,

82
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:14,440
and your mother died tragically.

83
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,120
Is that so?

84
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:26,280
For the murderer who killed my mother,

85
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:29,920
there is no one in the world who knows
it better than you do, Prime Minister.

86
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,200
How dare you!

87
00:11:37,412 --> 00:11:39,320
(Condolence)

88
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,040
Get out and kneel down.

89
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:54,144
(Su Mansion)

90
00:12:10,976 --> 00:12:13,160
The Master said
you shall leave Lady Yunqi alone.

91
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:15,600
You're just mad at Miss Su
for scolding you the other day.

92
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:17,480
But you were out there
gossiping about Lan,

93
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,640
forcing her to kill herself.

94
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:20,120
I dare not.

95
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,960
How dare you not
listen to the Master's order!

96
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,120
You!

97
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:52,600
I can help you take revenge.

98
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:06,048
Help me? My father is not a good man.

99
00:13:06,048 --> 00:13:07,524
And you are not a good man either.

100
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,760
You are trying to take advantage of me.

101
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:16,800
Don't make me your pawn.

102
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:22,160
Lady Yunqi, don't you realize
you have no way out?

103
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:27,800
No way out? I'll fight my way out.

104
00:13:42,724 --> 00:13:44,608
(Su Mansion)

105
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:53,800
(Accept your fate, Su Yunqi.)

106
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:12,400
Once the ink dries out,
the end is decided.

107
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:17,640
Then if the ink doesn't dry out,
the end can still be changed.

108
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,400
Now Su Luoluo has not
become the princess,

109
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,440
I still have a chance to survive.

110
00:14:25,284 --> 00:14:27,172
(Su Mansion)

111
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:31,640
(This will only make
things worse for you.)

112
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,640
Then I'll take a gamble.

113
00:14:55,236 --> 00:14:58,532
(Fortune Writer)

114
00:15:24,836 --> 00:15:31,232
♪Pen in hand,
fog disperses, light dawns♪

115
00:15:31,232 --> 00:15:37,056
♪Soft whispers, gentle moves,
tattered clothes♪

116
00:15:37,700 --> 00:15:43,680
♪Foot prints are marked by the world♪

117
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:49,312
♪Life is but a fleeting play♪

118
00:15:50,436 --> 00:15:56,128
♪Exposed plot in the tapestry of fate♪

119
00:15:56,836 --> 00:16:02,592
♪A thousand threads
in a gamble of life and death♪

120
00:16:03,332 --> 00:16:09,088
♪Reluctance and hesitation,
as wavering shadows of a lamp♪

121
00:16:09,728 --> 00:16:15,200
♪Breeze brings a whole night of rain♪

122
00:16:16,064 --> 00:16:21,984
♪From afar, I've drawn you on a scroll♪

123
00:16:22,496 --> 00:16:27,936
♪The inkstone,
finely carved with delicacy♪

124
00:16:28,736 --> 00:16:34,720
♪Love ignited, hair parted from comb♪

125
00:16:35,328 --> 00:16:40,448
♪The writer can never escape the pain♪
